{"type":"message","id":"26df2c82","parentId":"180e513b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:00:39.314Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2uq94v04i6zr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"claude-code-codingplan\nself-improving-agent\ntask_orchestrator\nv8_classifier\nv8_scorer\n---\n1password\napple-notes\napple-reminders\nbear-notes\nblogwatcher\nblucli\nbluebubbles\ncamsnap\ncanvas\nclawhub\ncoding-agent\ndiscord\neightctl\ngemini\ngh-issues\ngifgrep\ngithub\ngog\ngoplaces\nhealthcheck\nhimalaya\nimsg\nmcporter\nmodel-usage\nnano-pdf\nnode-connect\nnotion\nobsidian\nopenai-whisper\nopenai-whisper-api\nopenhue\noracle\nordercli\npeekaboo\nsag\nsession-logs\nsherpa-onnx-tts\nskill-creator\nslack\nsongsee\nsonoscli\nspotify-player\nsummarize\ntaskflow\ntaskflow-inbox-triage\nthings-mac\ntmux\ntrello\nvideo-frames\nvoice-call\nwacli\nweather\nxurl"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":47,"aggregated":"claude-code-codingplan\nself-improving-agent\ntask_orchestrator\nv8_classifier\nv8_scorer\n---\n1password\napple-notes\napple-reminders\nbear-notes\nblogwatcher\nblucli\nbluebubbles\ncamsnap\ncanvas\nclawhub\ncoding-agent\ndiscord\neightctl\ngemini\ngh-issues\ngifgrep\ngithub\ngog\ngoplaces\nhealthcheck\nhimalaya\nimsg\nmcporter\nmodel-usage\nnano-pdf\nnode-connect\nnotion\nobsidian\nopenai-whisper\nopenai-whisper-api\nopenhue\noracle\nordercli\npeekaboo\nsag\nsession-logs\nsherpa-onnx-tts\nskill-creator\nslack\nsongsee\nsonoscli\nspotify-player\nsummarize\ntaskflow\ntaskflow-inbox-triage\nthings-mac\ntmux\ntrello\nvideo-frames\nvoice-call\nwacli\nweather\nxurl","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776020439304}}
{"type":"message","id":"13073fed","parentId":"26df2c82","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:00:52.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has several custom skills installed in ~/.openclaw/skills/ and the openclaw npm package has many bundled skills. Let me list them more clearly.","thinkingSignature":"8c2f9e15da281be3dfc97914f0e3bbbf8c1f867faf8975710116a4c583bf6bf2"},{"type":"text","text":"**你的技能（~/.openclaw/skills/）—— 5个：**\n- `claude-code-codingplan` — Claude Code CLI + CodingPlan API 配置\n- `self-improving-agent` — 自我改进，记录错误和纠正\n- `task_orchestrator` — 任务编排器\n- `v8_classifier` — 意图分类（9种场景）\n- `v8_scorer` — 任务复杂度评分（DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA）\n\n**内置技能（openclaw 打包）—— 53个，分类看：**\n\n| 分类 | 技能 |\n|------|------|\n| 📱 平台 | apple-notes, apple-reminders, bear-notes, bluebubbles, imsg, things-mac |\n| 💬 消息 | discord, slack, wacli, xurl |\n| 🔧 开发 | coding-agent, gh-issues, github, mcporter, node-connect, session-logs, skill-creator |\n| 🌐 搜索/媒体 | blogwatcher, gifgrep, songsee, summarize, video-frames, weather, openai-whisper |\n| 🏠 智能家居 | blucli, openhue, sonoscli |\n| 🧠 记忆/任务 | taskflow, taskflow-inbox-triage, notion, obsidian, trello |\n| 🗣️ 语音 | openai-whisper-api, sag, sherpa-onnx-tts, voice-call |\n| 🖥️ 系统 | canvas, eightctl, gog, healthcheck, himalaya, nano-pdf, peekaboo, spotify-player, tmux |\n| 📦 工具 | 1password, blogwatcher, clawhub, gemini, model-usage, oracle, ordercli |\n\n大部分是平台/生态绑定技能（Apple Notes/Obsidian/Sonos 等），开箱即用的通用技能偏少。你装的 5 个里 `v8_classifier` + `v8_scorer` 明显是给任务编排用的，clawhub 技能装没装？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42314,"output":479,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60830,"cost":{"input":0.0126942,"output":0.0005748,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01435122}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776020439315,"responseId":"062b1ed64d111a79320dee6936fb0215"}}
