{"type":"message","id":"b6381d88","parentId":"870a6f95","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:08:33.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_m51qblilz5zg_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: OpenClaw\ntype: project\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [openclaw, ai-assistant, framework]\n---\n\n# 🦐 OpenClaw\n\n> OpenClaw AI 助手核心项目\n\n## 项目概览\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **类型** | AI 助手框架 |\n| **工作区** | `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace` |\n| **配置路径** | `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` |\n| **时区** | Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8) |\n| **状态** | 活跃运行中 |\n\n## 技术架构\n\n### 核心组件\n\n- **Gateway** (`localhost:18789`) — HTTP API 网关\n- **Router** (`localhost:3102`) — 任务评分 + 反向代理\n- **Context API** (`localhost:3101`) — 上下文管理\n- **Classifier** (`localhost:3104`) — 场景分类服务\n\n### 模型配置\n\n| 模型 | 用途 | 路径 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `codingplan/minimax-m2.5` | 主模型（当前运行时） | 默认 |\n| `volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro` | 备用模型 | 系统默认 |\n\n### 执行策略路由\n\n根据任务评分自动选择执行方式：\n\n| 分数区间 | 策略 | 超时 | 内存 |\n|----------|------|------|------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n## 消息处理流程\n\n```\n用户消息 \n  → v8_classifier (场景分类)\n  → v8_scorer (任务评分)\n  → 策略路由 (执执行方式)\n  → 结果返回\n```\n\n### 场景标签\n\n- `task_multi_step` — 多步骤任务\n- `fault_recovery` — 故障恢复\n- `chitchat` — 闲聊\n- `vague_request` — 模糊请求\n- `novice_user` — 新手用户\n- `expert_user` — 专业用户\n- `high_risk_automated` — 高风险自动化\n- `task_status_query` — 任务状态查询\n- `cancel_task` — 取消任务\n\n## 核心文件\n\n| 文件 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `AGENTS.md` | 任务编排、评分流程定义 |\n| `SOUL.md` | 行为约束、风险控制 |\n| `MEMORY.md` | 长期记忆入口 |\n| `IDENTITY.md` | AI 身份定义 |\n| `USER.md` | 用户画像 |\n\n## 常用命令\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status    # 网关状态\nopenclaw gateway restart   # 重启网关\nopenclaw gateway start     # 启动网关\nopenclaw gateway stop      # 停止网关\nopenclaw plugins list      # 插件列表\nopenclaw tasks             # 任务列表\n```\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[Skills]] — 已安装技能清单\n- [[Memory]] — 记忆系统\n- [[Model]] — 模型配置\n- [[Feishu]] — 飞书集成\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*- [[query]]\n- \n- [[practice]]\n- [[task-orchestrator]]\n- \n- [[llm-wiki-implementation]]\n- \n- [[version-control]]\n- \n- [[case-study]]\n- [[framework]]\n- \n- [[performance]]\n- [[search]]\n- [[wiki-evolution]]\n- [[error-handling]]\n- [[examples]]\n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- [[user]]\n- \n- [[config]]\n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- [[corrections]]\n- [[llm-wiki-original]]\n- [[skills]]\n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- [[addition-rules]]\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776020913816}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d2d95fd","parentId":"b6381d88","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:08:58.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture of this workspace. Let me summarize what I've learned:\n\n1. **Identity**: This is a workspace for \"小Claw\" (Little Claw), an OpenClaw AI assistant. There's been a recent identity unification (previously \"小六\" was deprecated in favor of \"小Claw\").\n\n2. **Core Architecture**: \n   - OpenClaw framework with Gateway at localhost:18789\n   - Task orchestrator with v3.0, with middleware: Router (3102), Context API (3101), Classifier (3104)\n   - 5-tier execution strategy based on task scoring\n   \n3. **Soul/System**: The system operates under a \"v9.5 Layered Constraint Architecture\" with risk-stratified protocols, prohibition-based governance (7 absolute prohibitions + mandatory execution items), and a personality layer that maintains directness and Chinese-language priority.\n\n4. **Memory System**: There's a multi-tier memory architecture comprising daily logs, entity archives, core entities, and long-term memory storage.\n\n5. **Workspace Structure**: The workspace maintains dual profile directories at both root and main levels, contains approximately 25 skills with some now obsolete like clawdbot-filesystem and task-orchestrator-v7, and logs significant events like the bootstrap断层 issue from 2026-04-12.\n\n6. **Active Development**: There's been recent cleanup and integration work including soul.md fusion and identity unification across the system.","thinkingSignature":"ba7d79343a517a4c70c07b6691ab685d1549d2cf4ee64b219b2b7553ba85c34b"},{"type":"text","text":"好，读完了，给你一个完整概览：\n\n---\n\n## Workspace 全貌\n\n### 身份系统\n**小Claw** — 2026-04-12 刚完成\"小六→小Claw\"统一。之前两套 identity 在打架（根目录 vs main/ 子目录），已融合。\n\n### 核心架构\n\n| 组件 | 地址 | 作用 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Gateway | localhost:18789 | HTTP API 网关 |\n| Router | localhost:3102 | 任务评分 + 反向代理 |\n| Context API | localhost:3101 | 上下文管理 |\n| Classifier | localhost:3104 | 场景分类（9类） |\n\n**执行策略**（根据评分自动路由）：\n```\n≤20 → DIRECT\n21-40 → STEP_ARCHIVE\n41-60 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT\n61-80 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n>80 → MEGA_TASK\n```\n\n### Soul v9.5 — 约束体系\n\n7条绝对禁令 + 风险分级（LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH/CRITICAL）+ 场景决策树。核心逻辑：\n- HIGH/CRITICAL 操作必须前置 `[!WARNING]`\n- 禁止臆造、禁止假装执行、禁止敷衍\n- 专业术语不降级，新手信号才带解释\n\n### 记忆系统\n\n```\nmemory/\n├── 2026-04-XX.md          # 每日日志（3月底~4月中）\n├── entities-archive/       # 80+ 归档实体（claude-code、wiki 等）\n├── entities/               # 核心25个实体页\n└── knowledge.md           # 固化知识\n```\n\n### 技能（25个，部分过时）\n\n活跃使用：\n- `v8_classifier` + `v8_scorer` — 场景分类+任务评分\n- `task_orchestrator` — 任务编排\n- `self-improving` — 自我改进\n- `proactivity` — 主动性行为\n\n**刚清理掉的（2026-04-12）**：\n- `clawdbot-filesystem/` ❌\n- `task-orchestrator-v7/` ❌\n- `openclaw-github-assistant/` ❌\n\n### 主要问题（从日志看）\n\n1. **Bootstrap 断层** — session key 是 `agent:main:main`，main/ 下无 MEMORY.md 导致加载失败，跨 session 连续性失效\n2. **SKILLS.md 和实际不符** — 文档还列着已删除的技能\n3. **双重文件结构** — 根目录和 main/ 子目录曾并存，已融合但可能有残留\n\n---\n\n一句话总结：**这是一个有完整自我认知系统的 AI 助手 workspace，有任务编排、记忆分层、风险控制，但刚经历了身份统一和技能清理，文档和实际状态还有小量不同步。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64823,"output":888,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83748,"cost":{"input":0.0194469,"output":0.0010655999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021594719999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776020913825,"responseId":"062b20b21c6f1c1110acfe2e0e62164f"}}
