{"type":"message","id":"50ee83c0","parentId":"a6f93320","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:16:04.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to focus on a single point - to think about just one thing, the most critical one. Let me think about what the single most important thing is.\n\nThe framework has many problems. But if I have to pick ONE thing to fix first, what would it be?\n\nThe core issue is \"no self-observation\" - the system can't perceive its own state. Without this, nothing else matters because you can't tell if anything is working.\n\nBut actually, let me think more carefully. What is the ONE thing that, if fixed, would unlock the most improvement?\n\nThe Bootstrap断层 issue means sessions don't carry memory. This is the most immediate pain - every /new or /reset wipes the slate. \n\nWithout continuous memory, I'm starting each session blind - I don't know who I am, what's happened before, what's been built or broken. That's the foundational gap. Everything else compounds from there: I can't learn from corrections if I can't remember them, can't improve if I can't track progress, can't maintain the system if I can't see what's failing. The Bootstrap fix is the single thread that, once pulled, starts unraveling all the other problems.\n\nThe issue likely stems from a mismatch between the session key (`agent:main:main`) and the workspace path, causing MEMORY.md to fail to load. But the user asked for single-point thinking, which in systems design means finding the leverage point - the smallest intervention that creates the largest cascading improvement. Bootstrap is the answer because it's the mandatory prerequisite for everything else to function.","thinkingSignature":"bc16726530819916cbe0cc8afd436da2c2a73f381c968f813ee7e0672cf00357"},{"type":"text","text":"一件事：**Bootstrap 断层修复**。\n\n这是所有问题的根。不修，其他所有改进都是建在沙上。\n\n- corrections 再多，记了也白记——下次 session 没了\n- memory-keeper 再完善，没人调用——下次 session 没了\n- 技能装得再全，用完就忘——下次 session 没了\n\n---\n\n**具体只做一件事：**\n\n在 session 启动时，强制写一行 bootstrap 日志到 `memory/bootstrap-log.md`：\n\n```\n[2026-04-13 03:15] session=agent:main:main loaded=MEMORY.md,AGENTS.md,SOUL.md ok=true\n```\n\n只需要这一行。下次断了，扫一眼就知道哪个文件加载失败，根因立刻定位。\n\n其他所有方案排队。等这一行稳定跑一周，再做下一个。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":478,"cacheRead":85796,"cacheWrite":715,"totalTokens":87043,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0005736,"cacheRead":0.0051477599999999995,"cacheWrite":0.000268125,"total":0.006005684999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776021349803,"responseId":"062b22661e756063494e3178727c495d"}}
