{"type":"message","id":"498e4419","parentId":"fa67ec81","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:18:43.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No cron jobs for memory-keeper. Let me check the health-check.py and other scripts.","thinkingSignature":"2c41e99b6ea81c5353a4c2d86543cabeb7ab4b54f1189cf6ee2b66e5bbb7da3b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pnkru91engls_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_keeper.sh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pnkru91engls_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/health-check.py | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":72913,"output":96,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91046,"cost":{"input":0.021873899999999998,"output":0.0001152,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023071319999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021520361,"responseId":"062b231083d7b56853877153493d64fe"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ec23aa0","parentId":"498e4419","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:18:43.234Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pnkru91engls_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n#===============================================================================\n# memory_keeper.sh - 记忆管理员 Agent (增强版)\n#\n# 功能：\n# 1. 读取 memory/ 下所有文件\n# 2. 合并重复信息\n# 3. 删除过期条目（根据 [expires:] 标记）\n# 4. 将临时对话中有价值的信息写入 ephemeral/\n# 5. 更新 MEMORY.md 索引\n# 6. [NEW] 从归档 session 中提取有价值信息到长期记忆\n#\n# 运行: ./memory_keeper.sh\n#===============================================================================\n\nset -e\n\nMEMORY_ROOT=\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace\"\nSESSION_ROOT=\"$HOME/.openclaw/sessions\"\nMEMORY_DIR=\"$MEMORY_ROOT/memory\"\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nYESTERDAY=$(date -d \"yesterday\" +%Y-%m-%d)\n\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nBLUE='\\033[0;34m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\nlog() { echo -e \"${GREEN}[$(date +%H:%M:%S)]${NC} $1\"; }\nwarn() { echo -e \"${YELLOW}[$(date +%H:%M:%S)]${NC} $1\"; }\ninfo() { echo -e \"${BLUE}[$(date +%H:%M:%S)]${NC} $1\"; }\n\necho \"========================================\"\necho \"  Memory Keeper (Enhanced) - $TODAY\"\necho \"========================================\"\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 1. 扫描各模块文件\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"📂 扫描记忆文件...\"\nfind \"$MEMORY_DIR\" -name \"*.md\" -type f | grep -v \".gitkeep\" | while read f; do\n    echo \"   - $(basename $f)\"\ndone\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 2. 检查过期条目\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"🔍 检查过期条目...\"\nEXPIRED_COUNT=0\nwhile IFS=: read -r file line content; do\n    if [[ -n \"$file\" ]]; then\n        expire_date=$(echo \"$content\" | grep -oP 'expires: \\K[0-9-]+')\n        if [[ \"$expire_date\" < \"$TODAY\" ]] && [[ -n \"$expire_date\" ]]; then\n            warn \"   过期: $(basename $file)#L$line\"\n            EXPIRED_COUNT=$((EXPIRED_COUNT + 1))\n        fi\n    fi\ndone < <(grep -rn \"expires:\" \"$MEMORY_DIR\" 2>/dev/null || true)\n\nif [[ $EXPIRED_COUNT -eq 0 ]]; then\n    log \"   ✅ 无过期条目\"\nelse\n    warn \"   共 $EXPIRED_COUNT 个过期条目待处理\"\nfi\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 3. 检查 ephemeral 目录\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"📋 检查临时记忆目录...\"\nEPHEMERAL_COUNT=$(find \"$MEMORY_DIR/ephemeral\" -name \"*.md\" -type f 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nlog \"   临时文件: $EPHEMERAL_COUNT 个\"\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 4. [NEW] 从归档 session 提取有价值信息\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"🧠 从归档 session 提取知识...\"\n\nSESSION_EXTRACT_FILE=\"$MEMORY_DIR/ephemeral/session_extract_$TODAY.md\"\n\n# 查找最近的归档 session（最近 3 天）\nfind \"$SESSION_ROOT\" -name \"*.json\" -mtime -3 -type f 2>/dev/null | head -5 | while read session_file; do\n    # 提取包含知识点的对话（如包含\"记住\"、\"学会\"、\"偏好\"等关键词）\n    grep -i \"记住\\|学会\\|偏好\\|规则\\|喜欢\\|讨厌\\|以后都\\|要使用\\|用.*不要\" \"$session_file\" 2>/dev/null | head -10 >> \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\" || true\ndone\n\n# 去重并写入\nif [[ -f \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\" ]]; then\n    if [[ -s \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\" ]]; then\n        {\n            echo \"# Session 知识提取 - $TODAY\"\n            echo \"\"\n            echo \"从近期的 session 归档中提取的有价值信息：\"\n            echo \"\"\n        } > \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE\"\n        \n        # 进一步提取关键词（JSON 中提取 message 内容）\n        cat \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\" | grep -oP '\"text\":\"[^\"]+' | sed 's/\"text\":\"//' | sed 's/\\\\n/ /g' | grep -v \"^system\" | sort -u >> \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE\"\n        \n        log \"   ✅ 提取了 session 知识到: $(basename $SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE)\"\n        \n        # 统计\n        EXTRACT_LINES=$(wc -l < \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE\")\n        log \"   📊 提取行数: $EXTRACT_LINES\"\n    else\n        log \"   ℹ️ 无新知识可提取\"\n    fi\n    rm -f \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\"\nelse\n    log \"   ℹ️ 无近期 session 可分析\"\nfi\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 5. 合并 ephemeral 到主记忆\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"🔄 检查是否需要合并 ephemeral...\"\nif [[ $EPHEMERAL_COUNT -gt 0 ]]; then\n    # 检查 ephemeral 是否有足够内容需要合并\n    EPHEMERAL_LINES=$(find \"$MEMORY_DIR/ephemeral\" -name \"*.md\" -exec cat {} \\; 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    if [[ $EPHEMERAL_LINES -gt 20 ]]; then\n        warn \"   ℹ️ ephemeral 有 $EPHEMERAL_LINES 行，可能需要手动 review 后合并\"\n    else\n        log \"   ✅ ephemeral 内容较少，暂不合并\"\n    fi\nfi\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 6. 更新 MEMORY.md 时间戳\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"📝 更新 MEMORY.md 时间戳...\"\nsed -i \"s/last_updated:.*/last_updated: ${TODAY}T$(date +%H:%M:%S)+08:00/\" \"$MEMORY_ROOT/MEMORY.md\"\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 7. 生成报告\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"  整理完成 - $TODAY\"\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"📊 总结：\"\nlog \"   - 过期条目: $EXPIRED_COUNT\"\nlog \"   - 临时文件: $EPHEMERAL_COUNT\"\nlog \"   - Session 提取: $([[ -f \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE\" ]] && echo \"是\" || echo \"否\")\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":59,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n#===============================================================================\n# memory_keeper.sh - 记忆管理员 Agent (增强版)\n#\n# 功能：\n# 1. 读取 memory/ 下所有文件\n# 2. 合并重复信息\n# 3. 删除过期条目（根据 [expires:] 标记）\n# 4. 将临时对话中有价值的信息写入 ephemeral/\n# 5. 更新 MEMORY.md 索引\n# 6. [NEW] 从归档 session 中提取有价值信息到长期记忆\n#\n# 运行: ./memory_keeper.sh\n#===============================================================================\n\nset -e\n\nMEMORY_ROOT=\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace\"\nSESSION_ROOT=\"$HOME/.openclaw/sessions\"\nMEMORY_DIR=\"$MEMORY_ROOT/memory\"\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nYESTERDAY=$(date -d \"yesterday\" +%Y-%m-%d)\n\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nBLUE='\\033[0;34m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\nlog() { echo -e \"${GREEN}[$(date +%H:%M:%S)]${NC} $1\"; }\nwarn() { echo -e \"${YELLOW}[$(date +%H:%M:%S)]${NC} $1\"; }\ninfo() { echo -e \"${BLUE}[$(date +%H:%M:%S)]${NC} $1\"; }\n\necho \"========================================\"\necho \"  Memory Keeper (Enhanced) - $TODAY\"\necho \"========================================\"\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 1. 扫描各模块文件\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"📂 扫描记忆文件...\"\nfind \"$MEMORY_DIR\" -name \"*.md\" -type f | grep -v \".gitkeep\" | while read f; do\n    echo \"   - $(basename $f)\"\ndone\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 2. 检查过期条目\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"🔍 检查过期条目...\"\nEXPIRED_COUNT=0\nwhile IFS=: read -r file line content; do\n    if [[ -n \"$file\" ]]; then\n        expire_date=$(echo \"$content\" | grep -oP 'expires: \\K[0-9-]+')\n        if [[ \"$expire_date\" < \"$TODAY\" ]] && [[ -n \"$expire_date\" ]]; then\n            warn \"   过期: $(basename $file)#L$line\"\n            EXPIRED_COUNT=$((EXPIRED_COUNT + 1))\n        fi\n    fi\ndone < <(grep -rn \"expires:\" \"$MEMORY_DIR\" 2>/dev/null || true)\n\nif [[ $EXPIRED_COUNT -eq 0 ]]; then\n    log \"   ✅ 无过期条目\"\nelse\n    warn \"   共 $EXPIRED_COUNT 个过期条目待处理\"\nfi\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 3. 检查 ephemeral 目录\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"📋 检查临时记忆目录...\"\nEPHEMERAL_COUNT=$(find \"$MEMORY_DIR/ephemeral\" -name \"*.md\" -type f 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nlog \"   临时文件: $EPHEMERAL_COUNT 个\"\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 4. [NEW] 从归档 session 提取有价值信息\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"🧠 从归档 session 提取知识...\"\n\nSESSION_EXTRACT_FILE=\"$MEMORY_DIR/ephemeral/session_extract_$TODAY.md\"\n\n# 查找最近的归档 session（最近 3 天）\nfind \"$SESSION_ROOT\" -name \"*.json\" -mtime -3 -type f 2>/dev/null | head -5 | while read session_file; do\n    # 提取包含知识点的对话（如包含\"记住\"、\"学会\"、\"偏好\"等关键词）\n    grep -i \"记住\\|学会\\|偏好\\|规则\\|喜欢\\|讨厌\\|以后都\\|要使用\\|用.*不要\" \"$session_file\" 2>/dev/null | head -10 >> \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\" || true\ndone\n\n# 去重并写入\nif [[ -f \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\" ]]; then\n    if [[ -s \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\" ]]; then\n        {\n            echo \"# Session 知识提取 - $TODAY\"\n            echo \"\"\n            echo \"从近期的 session 归档中提取的有价值信息：\"\n            echo \"\"\n        } > \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE\"\n        \n        # 进一步提取关键词（JSON 中提取 message 内容）\n        cat \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\" | grep -oP '\"text\":\"[^\"]+' | sed 's/\"text\":\"//' | sed 's/\\\\n/ /g' | grep -v \"^system\" | sort -u >> \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE\"\n        \n        log \"   ✅ 提取了 session 知识到: $(basename $SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE)\"\n        \n        # 统计\n        EXTRACT_LINES=$(wc -l < \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE\")\n        log \"   📊 提取行数: $EXTRACT_LINES\"\n    else\n        log \"   ℹ️ 无新知识可提取\"\n    fi\n    rm -f \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE.tmp\"\nelse\n    log \"   ℹ️ 无近期 session 可分析\"\nfi\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 5. 合并 ephemeral 到主记忆\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"🔄 检查是否需要合并 ephemeral...\"\nif [[ $EPHEMERAL_COUNT -gt 0 ]]; then\n    # 检查 ephemeral 是否有足够内容需要合并\n    EPHEMERAL_LINES=$(find \"$MEMORY_DIR/ephemeral\" -name \"*.md\" -exec cat {} \\; 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    if [[ $EPHEMERAL_LINES -gt 20 ]]; then\n        warn \"   ℹ️ ephemeral 有 $EPHEMERAL_LINES 行，可能需要手动 review 后合并\"\n    else\n        log \"   ✅ ephemeral 内容较少，暂不合并\"\n    fi\nfi\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 6. 更新 MEMORY.md 时间戳\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"📝 更新 MEMORY.md 时间戳...\"\nsed -i \"s/last_updated:.*/last_updated: ${TODAY}T$(date +%H:%M:%S)+08:00/\" \"$MEMORY_ROOT/MEMORY.md\"\n\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 7. 生成报告\n#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"  整理完成 - $TODAY\"\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"📊 总结：\"\nlog \"   - 过期条目: $EXPIRED_COUNT\"\nlog \"   - 临时文件: $EPHEMERAL_COUNT\"\nlog \"   - Session 提取: $([[ -f \"$SESSION_EXTRACT_FILE\" ]] && echo \"是\" || echo \"否\")\"","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776021523223}}
{"type":"message","id":"972a00f9","parentId":"2ec23aa0","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:18:43.249Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pnkru91engls_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"OpenClaw 健康检查 - 让我更鲁棒\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport json\nimport requests\n\nOLLAMA_URL = \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\"\nDB_FILE = os.environ.get(\"HOME\") + \"/.openclaw/memory/vectors.json\"\n\ndef check_ollama():\n    try:\n        r = requests.get(f\"{OLLAMA_URL}/api/tags\", timeout=5)\n        models = [m['name'] for m in r.json().get('models', [])]\n        has_bge = any('bge' in m.lower() for m in models)\n        return {\"status\": \"OK\", \"models\": len(models), \"has_bge\": has_bge}\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"status\": \"FAIL\", \"error\": str(e)}\n\ndef check_memory():\n    try:\n        with open(DB_FILE) as f:\n            db = json.load(f)\n        return {\"status\": \"OK\", \"count\": len(db.get(\"memories\", []))}\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"status\": \"FAIL\", \"error\": str(e)}\n\ndef check_openclaw():\n    try:\n        r = requests.get(\"http://127.0.0.1:18789/health\", timeout=5)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":70,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"OpenClaw 健康检查 - 让我更鲁棒\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport json\nimport requests\n\nOLLAMA_URL = \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\"\nDB_FILE = os.environ.get(\"HOME\") + \"/.openclaw/memory/vectors.json\"\n\ndef check_ollama():\n    try:\n        r = requests.get(f\"{OLLAMA_URL}/api/tags\", timeout=5)\n        models = [m['name'] for m in r.json().get('models', [])]\n        has_bge = any('bge' in m.lower() for m in models)\n        return {\"status\": \"OK\", \"models\": len(models), \"has_bge\": has_bge}\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"status\": \"FAIL\", \"error\": str(e)}\n\ndef check_memory():\n    try:\n        with open(DB_FILE) as f:\n            db = json.load(f)\n        return {\"status\": \"OK\", \"count\": len(db.get(\"memories\", []))}\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"status\": \"FAIL\", \"error\": str(e)}\n\ndef check_openclaw():\n    try:\n        r = requests.get(\"http://127.0.0.1:18789/health\", timeout=5)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776021523235}}
{"type":"message","id":"4de339cb","parentId":"972a00f9","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:18:55.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a very clear picture. The user has all the infrastructure in place:\n\n1. **elite-longterm-memory** skill - very comprehensive, 6-layer memory system\n2. **memory-keeper** script - fully written, ready to run\n3. **health-check.py** - checks Ollama, memory vectors, OpenClaw health\n4. **cron jobs** - no memory keeper or health-check cron is set up\n\nThe problem is crystal clear:\n- All the scripts and skills EXIST\n- They're NOT scheduled in cron\n- Nothing runs automatically\n\nThis is the answer to \"I need fully automatic, I remember there's an installed skill\":","thinkingSignature":"37cc2f96e0badedb567c4809c4f503e1057cdb3201167c81effa01821ff2e08b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n现在清楚了。你其实**已经有全套东西**：\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `elite-longterm-memory` 技能 | ✅ 装好了（6层记忆体系） |\n| `memory-keeper.sh` | ✅ 写好了 |\n| `health-check.py` | ✅ 写好了 |\n| `self-improving` 技能 | ✅ 装好了 |\n| **Cron 触发器** | ❌ **一个都没配** |\n\n---\n\n**你缺的不是技能，是没人上发条。**\n\nscripts 目录里有 `memory_keeper.sh`、`health-check.py`、`auto-learn-7h.sh`……全准备好了，就是没有 crontab 条目让它们自动跑。\n\n---\n\n**实现全自动，只需要一步：**\n\n给我 crontab 列表，我帮你把该自动的全部加上定时触发。\n\n你现在最想要哪个自动？\n1. **记忆自动整理** — `memory_keeper.sh` 每日跑\n2. **健康检查** — `health-check.py` 每5分钟跑，异常时告警\n3. **自我改进闭环** — corrections 有新条目时自动触发处理\n4. **session bootstrap 日志** — 每次启动写一行到日志\n\n一个一个来还是全加？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74733,"output":397,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93167,"cost":{"input":0.0224199,"output":0.0004764,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023978519999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776021523252,"responseId":"062b23132d7da607b9680d17822fb98c"}}
