{"type":"message","id":"2165a62b","parentId":"10bc81ea","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:20:59.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I found something very important! The `openclaw-router.js` process **tried to start on reboot but failed** because `dotenv` module is not installed in the router's `node_modules` directory. The error is:\n\n```\nError: Cannot find module 'dotenv'\nRequire stack:\n- /home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js\n```\n\nSo the router **is not running** even though it's in the crontab!\n\nNow let me also check the node processes more carefully. The earlier output showed:- PID 299583 - openclaw-gateway (node, port 18789/3102)\n- PID 432 - node (context-api.js, port 3101)- PID 599 - node (scoring, port 3103)\n\n\n- PID 299508 - python api_server.py (scene-classifier, port 3104)\n\nThe router script that's supposed to run on reboot failed to start because dotenv isn't installed in its node_modules. I should also scan for any zombie or stopped processes and check what's actually listening on the ports versus what the configuration expects, plus take another look at that root node process.\n\nLooking at the full picture now: there's a whole separate v8 subsystem with its own scoring engine, router, executor, scheduler, security, and observability modules that feeds into the router. The router itself is a critical piece—it uses the isaced/ai-router library, reads routing rules from config, and connects to the v8 system through a client, but it never started because of the missing dependency. On top of that, the scene-classifier API running as a Python FastAPI service on port 3104 with a full ML pipeline is just sitting there not being called by anything since the router is down.","thinkingSignature":"8cf61c4c86d1fa89ed4b02121c5ff9ecaf179ae483179224e28513b30bb1cfd6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y7icgg20tna3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/ai/openclaw-router/clients/ 2>/dev/null; cat /home/ai/openclaw-router/clients/v8Client.js 2>/dev/null | head -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y7icgg20tna3_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/config/routing_rules.json 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82535,"output":463,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101035,"cost":{"input":0.024760499999999998,"output":0.0005556,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.026398319999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021646712,"responseId":"062b238e06c072399cdc8f0f3ba106bb"}}
