{"type":"message","id":"250952fe","parentId":"ccdc8363","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:21:04.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a much fuller picture. The `openclaw-router/` directory is supposed to have a `clients/v8Client.js` but it's missing/not shown. This is significant.\n\nAlso, the routing_rules.json shows that there are supposed to be multiple agents: `fast_agent` and `deep_agent` with routing based on keyword matching and classifier labels. But where are these agents defined? The crontab also shows that the openclaw-router failed to start.\n\nLet me also check the workspace_backup directory since it had a scene-classifier copy.","thinkingSignature":"7c7aec60e7d2692efac81b92241bc10ceda1477fe08cc856e6eb46688150db15"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zmt9lm3i9z73_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/ai/workspace_backup/ 2>/dev/null | head -20; echo \"---\"; ls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace_backup/ 2>/dev/null | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zmt9lm3i9z73_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/logs/v8.log 2>/dev/null | tail -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83273,"output":222,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101532,"cost":{"input":0.024981899999999998,"output":0.00026639999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.026330519999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021659192,"responseId":"062b239afb28e0d6d8755eadfe301acf"}}
