{"type":"message","id":"b3d3ae3f","parentId":"e1c61edb","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:21:12.057Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the complete picture:\n\n**v8 system (v8.0) status:**\n- Started on 2026-04-10T11:07:35\n- Ran until 2026-04-10T15:10:17 (about 4 hours)\n- Then gracefully shut down (SIGTERM)\n- **Has not been running since April 10**\n\n**workspace_backup:**\n- Full backup of the workspace from some earlier time\n- Contains: AGENTS.md, BRAIN.md, CLAUDE.md, FINAL_REPORT.md, HEARTBEAT.md, IDENTITY.md, MEMORY.md, SKILLS.md, SOUL.md, TOOLS.md, USER.md, memory/, scripts/, self-improving/, etc.\n\n\n- The openclaw-router tried to restart on reboot but crashed immediately due to a missing dotenv dependency\n- There's also a separate v8 system running as a scoring service on port 3103, independent of the main workspace skills\n\nThe real problem is that the openclaw-router—which should be handling the intelligent routing between fast and deep agents—is completely down because of that dependency issue. What's interesting is that the v8 system did start back on April 10 and ran for a few hours before shutting down gracefully, so it was working at some point.\n\nSince the router isn't running, the v8 services don't have anything feeding them requests anymore. I need to look more closely at what's actually in the v8 subsystem and what the context/executor modules are doing to understand the full scope of what's broken.","thinkingSignature":"29fd6d3ff81f61eaaa13d8adf263d0214eb77495719299d9777754622beba7c5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kwkg10s73w9w_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/index.js 2>/dev/null | head -50"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kwkg10s73w9w_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/logs/rule-tuner.log 2>/dev/null | tail -10; echo \"---\"; cat /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/logs/strategy-analyzer.log 2>/dev/null | tail -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83885,"output":435,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102357,"cost":{"input":0.0251655,"output":0.000522,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02676972}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021664369,"responseId":"062b239f6b7b2abbb75584b016b42203"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f93af15","parentId":"b3d3ae3f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:21:12.178Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kwkg10s73w9w_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const express = require('express');\nconst { loadConfig } = require('./config');\nconst { TaskStore } = require('./persistence/TaskStore');\nconst { Scheduler } = require('./scheduler/Scheduler');\nconst { SandboxExecutor } = require('./executor/SandboxExecutor');\nconst { SecurityGateway } = require('./security/SecurityGateway');\nconst { createLogger } = require('./observability/logger');\nconst { HealthChecker } = require('./observability/health');\nconst { MetricsCollector } = require('./observability/metrics');\nconst { createApiRouter } = require('./router/api');\nconst { setupGracefulShutdown } = require('./utils/gracefulShutdown');\n\n(async () => {\n  // 1. 加载配置\n  const config = loadConfig();\n  const logger = createLogger(config);\n  logger.info('OpenClaw v8.0 starting...');\n\n  // 2. 初始化组件\n  const taskStore = new TaskStore(config);\n  await taskStore.init();\n  taskStore.on('error', (err) => logger.error({ err }, 'TaskStore error'));\n  taskStore.on('recovered', (count) => logger.info({ recovered: count }, 'Stale tasks recovered'));\n\n  const security = new SecurityGateway(config);\n  const executor = new SandboxExecutor(config, logger);\n  const metrics = new MetricsCollector();\n  const healthChecker = new HealthChecker(config, taskStore);\n\n  const scheduler = new Scheduler(taskStore, executor, config, logger);\n  scheduler.on('error', (err) => logger.error({ err }, 'Scheduler error'));\n  scheduler.on('task:started', ({ taskId }) => logger.info({ taskId }, 'Task started'));\n  scheduler.on('task:completed', ({ taskId }) => {\n    metrics.inc('tasks_completed');\n    logger.info({ taskId }, 'Task completed');\n  });\n  scheduler.on('task:failed', ({ taskId, error }) => {\n    metrics.inc('tasks_failed');\n    logger.warn({ taskId, error }, 'Task failed');\n  });\n  scheduler.on('draining', (count) => logger.info({ remaining: count }, 'Draining tasks'));\n\n  // 3. 启动调度器（不阻塞）\n  scheduler.start().catch(err => logger.fatal({ err }, 'Scheduler crashed'));\n\n  // 4. 创建 Express 应用\n  const app = express();\n  app.use(express.json({ limit: '10mb' }));\n  app.use((req, res, next) => {\n    logger.debug({ method: req.method, url: req.url }, 'Request');"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":61,"aggregated":"const express = require('express');\nconst { loadConfig } = require('./config');\nconst { TaskStore } = require('./persistence/TaskStore');\nconst { Scheduler } = require('./scheduler/Scheduler');\nconst { SandboxExecutor } = require('./executor/SandboxExecutor');\nconst { SecurityGateway } = require('./security/SecurityGateway');\nconst { createLogger } = require('./observability/logger');\nconst { HealthChecker } = require('./observability/health');\nconst { MetricsCollector } = require('./observability/metrics');\nconst { createApiRouter } = require('./router/api');\nconst { setupGracefulShutdown } = require('./utils/gracefulShutdown');\n\n(async () => {\n  // 1. 加载配置\n  const config = loadConfig();\n  const logger = createLogger(config);\n  logger.info('OpenClaw v8.0 starting...');\n\n  // 2. 初始化组件\n  const taskStore = new TaskStore(config);\n  await taskStore.init();\n  taskStore.on('error', (err) => logger.error({ err }, 'TaskStore error'));\n  taskStore.on('recovered', (count) => logger.info({ recovered: count }, 'Stale tasks recovered'));\n\n  const security = new SecurityGateway(config);\n  const executor = new SandboxExecutor(config, logger);\n  const metrics = new MetricsCollector();\n  const healthChecker = new HealthChecker(config, taskStore);\n\n  const scheduler = new Scheduler(taskStore, executor, config, logger);\n  scheduler.on('error', (err) => logger.error({ err }, 'Scheduler error'));\n  scheduler.on('task:started', ({ taskId }) => logger.info({ taskId }, 'Task started'));\n  scheduler.on('task:completed', ({ taskId }) => {\n    metrics.inc('tasks_completed');\n    logger.info({ taskId }, 'Task completed');\n  });\n  scheduler.on('task:failed', ({ taskId, error }) => {\n    metrics.inc('tasks_failed');\n    logger.warn({ taskId, error }, 'Task failed');\n  });\n  scheduler.on('draining', (count) => logger.info({ remaining: count }, 'Draining tasks'));\n\n  // 3. 启动调度器（不阻塞）\n  scheduler.start().catch(err => logger.fatal({ err }, 'Scheduler crashed'));\n\n  // 4. 创建 Express 应用\n  const app = express();\n  app.use(express.json({ limit: '10mb' }));\n  app.use((req, res, next) => {\n    logger.debug({ method: req.method, url: req.url }, 'Request');","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776021672164}}
