{"type":"message","id":"e479f00b","parentId":"6160c701","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:21:22.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture of the v8 system. It's a full task orchestration system with:\n\n1. **TaskStore** - persistence layer\n2. **Scheduler** - task scheduling\n3. **SandboxExecutor** - sandboxed task execution\n4. **SecurityGateway** - security filtering\n5. **MetricsCollector** - observability\n6. **HealthChecker** - health monitoring\n7. **Express API router** - HTTP API on port 3103\n\nAnd the v8.log shows it was last running on April 10 and then shut down. It has NOT been restarted since.\n\nNow let me summarize the full picture of what I found:\n\n\nThe v8 system is completely offline—v8.log confirms it hasn't been running since April 10 when it gracefully shut down, and there's no indication it was ever restarted. The openclaw-router also failed to start because dotenv isn't installed, so the entire orchestration layer is down. What's strange is that port 3103 is showing as listening on a node process with PID 599, which suggests something else might be using that port or the v8 system restarted at some point.\n\nThe scene-classifier API is also not responding on port 3104, even though the process appears to be running—I need to verify whether it's actually healthy or just stuck. Meanwhile, port 3101 is running the context-api.js successfully, and port 3102 is the gateway. But the scene-classifier process at PID 299508 is consuming 1.1GB of memory and has been alive since 02:29 today, which is concerning given that the router dependencies are broken and several key services seem to be in questionable states.","thinkingSignature":"659c2179cb25228ba74f303cffd93d507f66c8cfdd2a85dab2780b27e69c6f7c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f2j7bzqzp8ya_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:3104/health 2>/dev/null; echo \"---\"; curl -s http://localhost:3104/ 2>/dev/null | head -3"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f2j7bzqzp8ya_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/logs/openclaw.log 2>/dev/null | tail -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":84878,"output":449,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103364,"cost":{"input":0.025463399999999997,"output":0.0005388,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027084419999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021672200,"responseId":"062b23a80ec76f28d764fe7752eec1fa"}}
