{"type":"message","id":"7131d406","parentId":"cd9b5686","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:21:40.069Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the complete picture. The v8 system (PID 599) started again on 2026-04-12 at 04:45 and is currently running. It last shut down on April 11 at 18:46 and restarted on April 12 at 04:45.\n\nThe scene-classifier API (3104) is running and healthy.\n\nBut the openclaw-router is DOWN because of the missing dotenv module.\n\nLet me now compile a complete picture:\n\n**Running:**\n- Gateway (PID 299583) - ports 18789, 3102 ✅\n- Context API (PID 432) - port 3101 ✅\n\n\n- v8 Scoring/Router (PID 599) - port 3103 ✅\n- Scene Classifier (PID 299508) - port 3104 ✅\n\n**Not running:**\n- openclaw-router.js - crashed on reboot due to missing dotenv ❌\n\nThe system is running but the router that was supposed to route between fast/deep agents based on routing_rules.json is completely offline, which is a critical failure point.\n\nLooking at what should be happening: the router reads routing_rules.json and uses v8Client to connect to the v8 system, which has fast_agent and deep_agent configured. But the cron job that should restart the router on reboot failed because dotenv isn't installed, so the intelligent routing layer never came back up. The v8 subsystem is running standalone now without being called by anything.","thinkingSignature":"d8de34c6190a957268e7884df90c1cb40e25f6e06d4b43c8c21ee8b1b4878405"},{"type":"text","text":"找到的根本问题比你想象的深得多。\n\n---\n\n## 完整真相\n\n**实际在跑的服务：**\n\n| 服务 | 端口 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| OpenClaw Gateway | 18789/3102 | ✅ 正常 |\n| Context API (context-api.js) | 3101 | ✅ 正常 |\n| v8 核心系统 (PID 599) | 3103 | ✅ 昨晚 04:45 重启了 |\n| Scene Classifier (Python FastAPI) | 3104 | ✅ 正常 |\n\n**关键缺失——openclaw-router 死了：**\n\n```\nError: Cannot find module 'dotenv'\nRequire stack:\n- /home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js\n```\n\n`/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js` 在 reboot cron 里配置了开机自启，但**启动失败了**，原因：dotenv 模块没装。\n\n---\n\n## 真正的架构\n\n你设计的是**两层 AI 路由**：\n\n```\n用户请求\n    ↓\nopenclaw-router (port ?)\n    ↓ 读 routing_rules.json\n    ├─ fast_agent → v8 scoring (3103) → task 执行\n    └─ deep_agent → 直接模型\n```\n\nrouting_rules.json 里配了：\n- 代码/编程/重构 → fast_agent\n- 分析/推理/数学 → deep_agent\n- classifier 标签 → 走对应 agent\n\n**但 router 死了，规则没人用。**\n\n---\n\n## 你不知道的\n\n1. **v8 系统是一个完整的任务编排引擎** — SandboxExecutor + SecurityGateway + Scheduler + MetricsCollector + HealthChecker，全在这套代码里。但没人调用它。\n\n2. **scene-classifier 是独立的 ML pipeline** — PipelineOrchestrator + RuleClassifier，跑了但没人接。\n\n3. **workspace_backup 是全量备份** — 包含所有配置、记忆、脚本，是一个完整的workspace快照。\n\n4. **openclaw-router 有 clients/v8Client.js** — 连接 v8 系统的客户端，这个文件可能在也可能缺失。\n\n---\n\n## 现在怎么做\n\n一件事：**修复 openclaw-router 的 dotenv 依赖，让它能跑起来。**\n\n```bash\ncd /home/ai/openclaw-router && npm install dotenv\n```\n\n然后重启验证。其他的等你确认 router 活着再说。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86256,"output":775,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105068,"cost":{"input":0.0258768,"output":0.0009299999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027889019999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776021682458,"responseId":"062b23b2e098057efc9a236c30499b12"}}
