{"type":"message","id":"fa3099c3","parentId":"2ecf5ac9","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:22:59.095Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_td1al3rwdca6_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SKILL.md\n__init__.py\napi_server.py\nclassifier\ndata\nfeedback\ninterceptors\nlogs\nmodels\npipeline\npipeline.py\nrequirements.txt\nscripts\ntemplates\n# Scene Classifier - 场景分类器\n\n> 基于嵌入向量的轻量级场景分类系统\n\n## 模块结构\n\n```\nscene-classifier/\n├── SKILL.md                      # 本文件\n├── __init__.py                   # 主入口\n├── pipeline.py                   # Pipeline 编排器\n├── data/\n│   └── synthetic_training_data.py   # 训练数据构造\n├── classifier/\n│   └── scene_classifier.py          # 分类器模型\n├── templates/\n│   └── template_map.py               # 模板注入\n├── scripts/\n│   └── train_classifier.py           # 训练脚本\n└── feedback/"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":73,"aggregated":"SKILL.md\n__init__.py\napi_server.py\nclassifier\ndata\nfeedback\ninterceptors\nlogs\nmodels\npipeline\npipeline.py\nrequirements.txt\nscripts\ntemplates\n# Scene Classifier - 场景分类器\n\n> 基于嵌入向量的轻量级场景分类系统\n\n## 模块结构\n\n```\nscene-classifier/\n├── SKILL.md                      # 本文件\n├── __init__.py                   # 主入口\n├── pipeline.py                   # Pipeline 编排器\n├── data/\n│   └── synthetic_training_data.py   # 训练数据构造\n├── classifier/\n│   └── scene_classifier.py          # 分类器模型\n├── templates/\n│   └── template_map.py               # 模板注入\n├── scripts/\n│   └── train_classifier.py           # 训练脚本\n└── feedback/","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776021779084}}
{"type":"message","id":"aed79dc3","parentId":"fa3099c3","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:23:33.393Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the entire system. Let me write a deeply considered, comprehensive analysis.\n\nThe key insights:\n\n1. **Two complete systems** - there's the OpenClaw-native v8 scoring/classifier (ports 3103/3104) and the openclaw-router (a completely separate routing system built by the user). They're both trying to do routing but not integrated.\n\n2. **The openclaw-router is the critical failure point** - it's the traffic cop, it's dead, and no one noticed for potentially days/weeks.\n\n3. **The workspace has massive automation potential that's completely dormant** - scripts exist but almost none are cron-triggered.\n   \n4. **Memory is completely fragmented across dozens of places** - There's no coordination between the 6-layer memory architecture described in the skill and what's actually being used.\n\n5. **The v8 system has been running untouched since April 12** - It boots, runs, and does nothing because nothing routes to it.\n\n6. **Two workspace SKILLS.md files** - The workspace backup and main workspace have identical SKILLS.md, but both list deleted skills (clawdbot-filesystem, openclaw-github-assistant, task-orchestrator-v7). This means the workspace_backup might be from before the cleanup.\n\n7. **The workspace backup is 28M** - That's substantial, suggesting it hasn't been synced since before the cleanup when things were even messier.\n\n8. **The scene-classifier skill and the v8 scene-classifier are the same thing** - They're both at 3104.\n\n9. **The task_orchestrator skill (in workspace/skills) and the v8 system (at 3103) are different implementations** - The skill is middleware calling 3102/3101, while v8 is a completely separate Node.js system with its own scheduler and executor.\n\nThe real problem is architectural fragmentation. The user built two separate orchestration systems - openclaw-router handles the chat layer with express and ai-router, routing messages to different agents via routing rules, while the v8 system is a self-contained task orchestrator that runs independently. They don't connect to each other, they're not integrated with the gateway, and they might be doing completely different things.\n\nThe whole system is held together by conventions and human processes rather than automated workflows, so when one piece breaks, nothing fails visibly - it just silently stops working.","thinkingSignature":"468445e6d16c403fd6c7d221204c57e40ed724cf5af127f1bfb940469f77b4ec"},{"type":"text","text":"好，全面深度想完，说结论。\n\n---\n\n## 根本性问题：三层架构互相不知道对方存在\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                 你以为的系统                          │\n│   用户 → OpenClaw Gateway → AI → 回复                │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                 实际的三层碎片                        │\n│                                                     │\n│  Layer 1: OpenClaw Gateway (18789)                  │\n│          ← 这层活着，AI 在跑，session 在走            │\n│                                                     │\n│  Layer 2: openclaw-router (应该→3102→3103)          │\n│          ← 死了，没人知道                            │\n│                                                     │\n│  Layer 3: v8 系统 (3103 独立任务编排引擎)              │\n│          ← 活着，但没人用它                          │\n│          ← 自成一个闭环：Scheduler/Executor/Security  │\n│                                                     │\n│  断点：Layer 1 和 Layer 2 之间断了                  │\n│       Layer 2 死的时候 Layer 1 不知道                │\n│       Layer 3 完全独立运行，没人连                    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 真正的问题：架构没有连起来\n\n**openclaw-router 死因：** dotenv 模块缺失，service 配置了但跑不起来。这是表层。\n\n**深层原因：**\n1. openclaw-router 本该是 Gateway 和 v8 系统之间的流量分配器，但它和 3103 的 v8 引擎之间**没有真正的连接**——clients/v8Client.js 可能存在但不完整\n2. v8 系统（3103）和 OpenClaw Gateway（18789）是**两个独立进程**，没有官方的互联协议\n3. 3104 scene-classifier 被 Gateway 调用了（AGENTS.md 里写了），但 routing_rules.json 里的规则指向它，**而 router 死了所以规则也没人用**\n\n---\n\n## 被忽视的资产\n\n| 组件 | 实际价值 | 现状 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| v8 系统 (3103) | 完整任务编排引擎：SandboxExecutor + SecurityGateway + Scheduler | 跑了5天，在空转 |\n| workspace/scripts | 20+ 自动化脚本：lint/keeper/wiki/health | 只有一个天气在跑 |\n| elite-longterm-memory | 6层记忆体系（热/温/冷/归档/云端/Mem0） | 只用了\"文件层\" |\n| scene-classifier (3104) | ML pipeline，circuit breaker 设计 | 被调用了，但 router 死了一并失效 |\n| openclaw-router | @isaced/ai-router + 自定义规则引擎 | dotenv 缺失 |\n\n---\n\n## 结构性风险\n\n**风险1：单点失效不知道**\n- openclaw-router 死了 → 天气脚本继续跑 → 用户以为系统正常 → router 挂了没人发现\n- 没有监控，没有健康检查告警（health-check.py 存在但不在 cron 里）\n\n**风险2：记忆在积累但没有提炼**\n- 28M workspace，memory/ 下 80+ 实体归档\n- entities-archive/ 是垃圾堆，不是知识库\n- memory-keeper 写了但没人调度\n\n**风险3：v8 系统是孤儿**\n- 它有自己的 Scheduler、Executor、SecurityGateway、HealthChecker\n- 比 workspace 的 task_orchestrator 技能完整得多\n- 但它和主 session 系统之间没有 pipeline 连接\n\n---\n\n## 全局判断\n\n```\n你建了三套并行的\"智能系统\"：\n1. OpenClaw Gateway（会话控制）—— 实际在用\n2. openclaw-router（流量路由）—— 死了\n3. v8 任务引擎（任务执行）—— 在空转\n\n这三套之间没有可靠的连接协议。\n系统靠人工操作和约定在维持运转。\n```\n\n---\n\n## 最优先的一件事\n\n**把 openclaw-router 修复并验证它能连上 v8 系统。**\n\n验证方法：\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"task\":\"test\",\"text\":\"hello\"}'\n```\n\n如果返回正常 → router 可以重启。\n如果返回 404/500 → v8 系统的 API 路由和 router 客户端不匹配，需要对齐。\n\n之后才有资格谈\"全自动\"。现在连基础连通性都没确认。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86761,"output":1402,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106200,"cost":{"input":0.026028299999999997,"output":0.0016824,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028792919999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776021779099,"responseId":"062b2412c6e2cd9f4cc6614619e1fe4b"}}
