{"type":"message","id":"e0fe91a0","parentId":"c3b7b656","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:26:53.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So Feishu is NOT configured. The weather report script is trying to send to a Feishu chat, but it probably fails silently.\n\nNow let me compile the complete picture. Here's what I now know:\n\n**RUNNING PROCESSES:**\n1. `openclaw-gateway` (PID 299583) - Gateway on ports 18789 (HTTP) + 3102 (WS)\n2. `context-api.js` (PID 432) - Context API on 3101 ✅ RUNNING\n3. `v8 system` (PID 599) - v8 task engine on 3103 ✅ RUNNING\n4. `api_server.py` (PID 299508) - Scene Classifier Python on 3104 ✅ RUNNING but /classify returns 500\n\n\n5. `weather_report.sh` cron - trying to send to a Feishu channel that isn't configured\n\n**DEAD SERVICES (auto-restart loop):**\n6. `openclaw-router.service` - trying to start at boot, dying due to missing dotenv module\n7. `openclaw-ws-proxy.service` - same dotenv issue, plus ws-proxy.js is configured to connect to port 3108 which doesn't exist\n\n**CRON JOBS:**\n- `@reboot` - openclaw-router startup (fails silently)\n- `0 8 * * *` - weather report (fails because Feishu isn't set up)\n- `0 2 * * 0` - rule-tuner.js (has enough samples to run but v8 needs to verify)\n- `0 3 * * 0` - strategy-analyzer.js (same situation)\n\nI'm seeing critical failures across the system: the router and ws-proxy both need that dotenv module, the Scene Classifier endpoint is returning 500s, the weather reports are going to a non-existent Feishu channel, and there's a complete mismatch where ws-proxy points to port 3108 when the Gateway is actually on 18789.\n\nBeyond those, there's version skew between the workspace skills and the actual installed ones, a workspace backup that was created at some point but I need to understand why, an 80+ page memory archive that's grown without proper maintenance, and health-check.py is written but never actually running in production.","thinkingSignature":"8e30aff7e6a7fafe0cfacbea72b6bee3ab21eef4e370ebce7d797b59ac0a9691"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hjdwxlv3izwf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/ai/workspace_backup/ | head -5; echo \"---\"; du -sh /home/ai/workspace_backup/ 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hjdwxlv3izwf_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ | wc -l; echo \"---\"; ls /home/ai/.openclaw/skills/ 2>/dev/null | wc -l"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97422,"output":587,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116046,"cost":{"input":0.0292266,"output":0.0007044,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031013219999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776022002596,"responseId":"062b24f2cfba89041a13e1d89e32119c"}}
