{"type":"message","id":"6b0493d3","parentId":"c9593678","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:30:16.908Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me compile everything about the LLM setup:\n\n1. **Current model**: `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7` - reasoning=true, 204800 context, maxTokens 131072\n2. **Fallback chain**: 13 different models as fallbacks including deepseek-chat, deepseek-reasoner, ollama/qwen2.5:14b, volcengine models, etc.\n3. **Providers**: minimax, deepseek, ollama, volcengine-plan, codingplan\n4. **Feishu is configured** and enabled (with appId/appSecret)\n\n\n5. **LanceDB memory** is also enabled with bge-m3 embeddings through the memory-lancedb plugin\n6. **fast_agent and deep_agent** are set up as separate agents, though I'm not certain which one is handling my current conversation\n\nThe Gateway configuration looks solid with 13 fallbacks and LanceDB's vector search capabilities. The real issue is that the scene-classifier on 3104 is throwing 500 errors, so the routing never actually reaches the LLM layer—it fails before any model gets invoked.\n\nDigging into the routing_rules.json, I see it expects classifier labels from the router, but since the router is down, those labels never get generated. And there's a second bottleneck: the Gateway's hooks are trying to call both the classifier (3104/classify) and scorer (3103/api/score) for every message, but the Gateway itself doesn't have direct access to these—the router would normally handle that traffic management.","thinkingSignature":"6004f3da7bbb5a1be318f187306ec7acdf4a0e8c813a4b45796580bc7f7e4b5f"},{"type":"text","text":"现在LLM配置全清楚了。\n\n---\n\n## LLM 配置总览\n\n**当前运行模型：`minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`**\n- 推理模型（reasoning: true）\n- 204800 token context window\n- 131072 max output\n- 实际在用这个\n\n**Fallback 链（13个备选）：**\n```\nminimax/MiniMax-M2.7\n    ↓\ndeepseek/deepseek-chat\ndeepseek/deepseek-reasoner\nollama/qwen2.5:14b  (本地！172.23.96.1:11434)\ncodingplan/minimax-m2.5\nvolcengine-plan/ark-code-latest\nvolcengine-plan/doubao-seed-code\nvolcengine-plan/glm-4.7\nvolcengine-plan/deepseek-v3.2\nvolcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-code\nvolcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro\nvolcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-lite\nvolcengine-plan/minimax-m2.5\nvolcengine-plan/kimi-k2.5\n```\n\n**Provider 配置：**\n| Provider | 用途 | API |\n|----------|------|-----|\n| `minimax` | 主模型 | Anthropic Messages |\n| `deepseek` | 备选 | OpenAI Compatible |\n| `ollama` | 本地模型 | 172.23.96.1:11434 |\n| `volcengine-plan` | 国内备选 | OpenAI Compatible |\n| `codingplan` | 编码备选 | OpenAI Compatible |\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 实际问题\n\n**场景分类和任务评分没有进入 LLM 流程。**\n\nGateway hooks 里配置了：\n```json\n\"auto-score-classify\": { \"enabled\": true }\n```\n\n但 hooks 执行需要调用 3104/classify → 返回 500。\n\n这意味着**每次消息进来，分类步骤静默失败，路由决策退化为纯规则匹配**。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ LLM 侧真正好的部分\n\n1. **飞书已配置** — appId/appSecret 都在，Feishu plugin 加载了\n2. **LanceDB 向量记忆已启用** — bge-m3 embeddings，autoCapture + autoRecall 都开着\n3. **session 隔离正确** — `dmScope: \"per-channel-peer\"`（之前担心的多用户隐私问题已修复）\n4. **多 Agent 隔离** — fast_agent / deep_agent workspace 分离\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\nLLM 配置本身没问题——模型充足、fallback 链完整、飞书已接通、LanceDB 已启用。\n\n**真正的问题链路：**\n\n```\n用户消息\n    ↓\nGateway (hooks: auto-score-classify enabled)\n    ↓\n3104/classify → 500 Internal Server Error  ← 这里断了\n    ↓\n(v8_scorer 从未被调用)\n    ↓\n直接走默认 DIRECT 路由 → MiniMax-M2.7\n```\n\n3104 的 scene-classifier 坏了，导致整个\"分类→评分→路由\"智能决策树没有触发。所有消息都直接走默认路径，v8 引擎完全空转。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":101253,"output":1001,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120291,"cost":{"input":0.030375899999999997,"output":0.0012012,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03265932}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776022195912,"responseId":"062b25b3fe56e678753b8bcbaedbbf56"}}
