{"type":"message","id":"7d29b95b","parentId":"213077e2","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:21.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at the relevant files that might contain the LLM task related to entity pages.","thinkingSignature":"348d8326510774eff5a283f9ffdae088fb9a128758d3d3a5829ba92d3ddedd83"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sd27slt8xig7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/wiki-schema.md","limit":80}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sd27slt8xig7_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/llm-wiki.md","limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102583,"output":119,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120739,"cost":{"input":0.030774899999999997,"output":0.0001428,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031999919999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776022338090,"responseId":"062b26423e59cb53531a483428c4bbf5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0de84a45","parentId":"7d29b95b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:21.522Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sd27slt8xig7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: Wiki Schema\ntype: schema\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [schema, convention, wiki-structure]\n---\n\n# 📋 Wiki Schema\n\n> LLM Wiki 页面规范与工作流定义\n\n---\n\n## 1. 页面类型\n\n| 类型 | 文件名模式 | 示例 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| `entity` | `小写-连字符.md` | `openclaw.md`, `feishu.md` |\n| `concept` | `小写-连字符.md` | `llm-wiki.md` |\n| `process` | `小写-连字符.md` | `ingest.md`, `lint.md` |\n| `project` | `小写-连字符.md` | `claude-code.md` |\n\n---\n\n## 2. Frontmatter 规范\n\n```yaml\n---\ntitle: 页面标题 (中文)\ntype: entity|concept|process|project\nstatus: active|draft|archived\nlast_updated: YYYY-MM-DD\ntags: [tag1, tag2, tag3]\n---\n```\n\n### 字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 必填 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `title` | ✅ | 页面标题 |\n| `type` | ✅ | 页面类型 |\n| `status` | ✅ | 状态：活跃/草稿/归档 |\n| `last_updated` | ✅ | 最后更新日期 |\n| `tags` | 推荐 | 标签列表，便于检索 |\n\n---\n\n## 3. 页面结构模板\n\n### 3.1 Entity 页\n\n```markdown\n---\ntitle: {标题}\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: {日期}\ntags: [{标签}]\n---\n\n# {emoji} {标题}\n\n> 一句话描述\n\n## 概览\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| ... | ... |\n\n## 核心内容\n\n...\n\n## 相关页面\n\n-  — 描述\n```\n\n[129 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776022341507}}
{"type":"message","id":"18ad1f61","parentId":"0de84a45","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:21.532Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sd27slt8xig7_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: LLM Wiki Pattern\ntype: concept\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [llm-wiki, knowledge-base, pattern]\n---\n\n# 📚 LLM Wiki Pattern\n\n> LLM 驱动的个人知识库模式\n\n## 核心理念\n\n**不采用 RAG 模式，而是编译 (Compilation)**\n\n| RAG | LLM Wiki |\n|-----|----------|\n| 每次查询重新发现 | 知识已编译、持续积累 |\n| 无积累 | 交叉引用已建立 |\n| 无法处理复杂综合问题 | 多文档综合已有答案 |\n\n## 三层架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Raw Sources (不可变)                 │\n│ 文章、论文、对话、笔记               │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                   ↓ LLM 摄取\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Wiki (LLM 维护)                     │\n│ 实体页 + 概念页 + 交叉引用           │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                   ↓ LLM 维护\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Schema (CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md)      │\n│ 页面格式、workflow、约定            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Operations\n\n### 1. Ingest (摄取)\n\n1. 放入新 source 到 raw/\n2. LLM 读取，提取关键信息\n3. 写 summary 到 wiki\n4. 更新相关 entity/concept 页 (10-15 个)\n5. 追加 log\n\n### 2. Query (查询)\n\n1. 读 index 找相关页\n2. 读取页面内容\n3. 合成答案\n4. 好答案可写回 wiki\n\n### 3. Lint (检查)\n\n- 矛盾点检测\n- 过时信息标记\n- 孤儿页面检测\n- 缺失跨引用\n\n## 工具链建议\n\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| Obsidian | 本地 IDE |\n| Obsidian Web Clipper | 网页转 markdown |\n| qmd | 本地搜索 (BM25 + 向量) |\n| Marp | 幻灯片生成 |\n| Dataview | 动态查询 |\n\n## 与我的集成\n\n本次 (2026-04-11) 实践：\n\n| 阶段 | 完成 |\n\n[73 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776022341522}}
{"type":"message","id":"068cad09","parentId":"18ad1f61","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:25.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The LLM Wiki Pattern with \"Compilation\" approach. Let me read more about this and the actual implementation.","thinkingSignature":"8c75f8cb045e401025dfb0eff3ce7d2516629daa17a8aaf14fee58f0f64a9032"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0seo2es3zn1q_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/llm-wiki.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0seo2es3zn1q_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -rl \"摄.*入\\|ingest\\|写.*实体\\|entity.*生成\\|生成.*page\" /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/ 2>/dev/null | head -10; echo \"---\"; ls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/ | grep -i \"ingest\\|entity\\|wiki\\|auto\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103641,"output":160,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121838,"cost":{"input":0.0310923,"output":0.000192,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03236652}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776022341535,"responseId":"062b2645db2345934702db898315900e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e826910f","parentId":"068cad09","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:25.991Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0seo2es3zn1q_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: LLM Wiki Pattern\ntype: concept\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [llm-wiki, knowledge-base, pattern]\n---\n\n# 📚 LLM Wiki Pattern\n\n> LLM 驱动的个人知识库模式\n\n## 核心理念\n\n**不采用 RAG 模式，而是编译 (Compilation)**\n\n| RAG | LLM Wiki |\n|-----|----------|\n| 每次查询重新发现 | 知识已编译、持续积累 |\n| 无积累 | 交叉引用已建立 |\n| 无法处理复杂综合问题 | 多文档综合已有答案 |\n\n## 三层架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Raw Sources (不可变)                 │\n│ 文章、论文、对话、笔记               │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                   ↓ LLM 摄取\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Wiki (LLM 维护)                     │\n│ 实体页 + 概念页 + 交叉引用           │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                   ↓ LLM 维护\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Schema (CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md)      │\n│ 页面格式、workflow、约定            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Operations\n\n### 1. Ingest (摄取)\n\n1. 放入新 source 到 raw/\n2. LLM 读取，提取关键信息\n3. 写 summary 到 wiki\n4. 更新相关 entity/concept 页 (10-15 个)\n5. 追加 log\n\n### 2. Query (查询)\n\n1. 读 index 找相关页\n2. 读取页面内容\n3. 合成答案\n4. 好答案可写回 wiki\n\n### 3. Lint (检查)\n\n- 矛盾点检测\n- 过时信息标记\n- 孤儿页面检测\n- 缺失跨引用\n\n## 工具链建议\n\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| Obsidian | 本地 IDE |\n| Obsidian Web Clipper | 网页转 markdown |\n| qmd | 本地搜索 (BM25 + 向量) |\n| Marp | 幻灯片生成 |\n| Dataview | 动态查询 |\n\n## 与我的集成\n\n本次 (2026-04-11) 实践：\n\n| 阶段 | 完成 |\n|------|------|\n| 实体页创建 | 13 个 |\n| Wiki 结构 | ✅ 已搭建 |\n| Ingest 流程 | 定义完成 |\n| Lint 机制 | 待实现 |\n\n---\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[memory]] — 记忆系统\n- [[ingest]] — 摄取流程\n- [[Claude Code]] — 参考的学习项目\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-11*- [[query]]\n- \n- [[practice]]\n- \n- [[llm-wiki-implementation]]\n- \n- [[version-control]]\n- \n- [[case-study]]\n- [[framework]]\n- \n- [[performance]]\n- [[search]]\n- [[wiki-evolution]]\n- [[error-handling]]\n- [[examples]]\n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- [[user]]\n- \n- [[config]]\n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- [[corrections]]\n- [[llm-wiki-original]]\n- [[skills]]\n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- [[addition-rules]]\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776022345981}}
{"type":"message","id":"d744f158","parentId":"e826910f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:26.003Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0seo2es3zn1q_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop.sh\n---\nauto-learn-7h.sh\nauto-lint.sh\nwiki-7h-loop-v2.sh\nwiki-7h-loop.sh\nwiki-auto-learn.py\nwiki-deep-learn-7h.sh\nwiki-think-7h.sh\nwiki-trigger.sh"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":49,"aggregated":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop.sh\n---\nauto-learn-7h.sh\nauto-lint.sh\nwiki-7h-loop-v2.sh\nwiki-7h-loop.sh\nwiki-auto-learn.py\nwiki-deep-learn-7h.sh\nwiki-think-7h.sh\nwiki-trigger.sh","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776022345991}}
{"type":"message","id":"1fae7ce1","parentId":"d744f158","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:34.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it. There are wiki auto-learn scripts. Let me look at the key ones to understand what the LLM task for entity pages was about.","thinkingSignature":"b11531ac01b77787f01f791434ccb1ebfd3694c5306179ff7a114660e17514f3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_04z4j2csibxt_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py","limit":80}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_04z4j2csibxt_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/wiki-evolution.md","limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104649,"output":124,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122810,"cost":{"input":0.0313947,"output":0.00014879999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03262572}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776022346005,"responseId":"062b2649211210fb26f294c19f1c3d87"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d71c09ad","parentId":"1fae7ce1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:34.532Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_04z4j2csibxt_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nLLM Wiki Auto-Learning Framework\n高鲁棒、高质量、高性能自动化学习循环\n\n基于需求 + LLM Wiki 原文设计\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport time\nimport subprocess\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 配置\nWORKSPACE = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities\"\nRAW_SOURCES_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/raw\"\nLOG_FILE = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/log.md\"\nARCHIVE_DIR = f\"{WORKSPACE}/memory/entities-archive\"\n\n# LLM Wiki 原文核心要点\nCORE_PRINCIPLES = {\n    \"not_rag\": \"不是RAG，是增量构建持久wiki\",\n    \"compile_once\": \"知识编译一次，持续更新\",\n    \"touch_10_15\": \"一个source触发10-15页更新\",\n    \"maintenance_zero\": \"维护成本接近零\",\n    \"human_role\": \"人负责选源、提问、思考\",\n    \"llm_role\": \"LLM负责执行维护\",\n    \"query_writeback\": \"好答案写回wiki\",\n    \"memex\": \"LLM解决维护问题\"\n}\n\nclass WikiAutoLearn:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.stats = {\n            \"iterations\": 0,\n            \"ingested\": 0,\n            \"fixed\": 0,\n            \"queries\": 0,\n            \"errors\": 0\n        }\n        \n    def log(self, msg):\n        \"\"\"带时间戳的日志\"\"\"\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        print(f\"[{timestamp}] {msg}\")\n        \n    def scan_sources(self):\n        \"\"\"1. 扫描知识源 (Ingest)\"\"\"\n        sources = []\n        \n        # 扫描 docs/\n        docs_dir = Path(f\"{WORKSPACE}/docs\")\n        if docs_dir.exists():\n            for f in docs_dir.glob(\"*.md\"):\n                sources.append((\"doc\", str(f)))\n        \n        # 扫描 skills/\n        skills_dir = Path(f\"{WORKSPACE}/skills\")\n        if skills_dir.exists():\n            for f in skills_dir.iterdir():\n                if f.is_dir():\n                    sources.append((\"skill\", str(f)))\n        \n        return sources\n    \n    def synthesize(self, source):\n        \"\"\"2. 思考合成 (Synthesize) - 对照原文核心\"\"\"\n        source_type, source_path = source\n        name = Path(source_path).name\n        \n        # 对照 LLM Wiki 原文核心\n        analysis = {\n            \"name\": name,\n            \"type\": source_type,\n            \"value\": \"unknown\",\n            \"relevance\": \"unknown\",\n            \"action\": \"skip\"\n\n[169 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776022354519}}
{"type":"message","id":"42514f75","parentId":"d71c09ad","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:34.545Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_04z4j2csibxt_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: Wiki Evolution\ntype: process\nstatus: draft\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [evolution, iteration, growth]\n---\n\n# 📈 Wiki Evolution\n\n> Wiki 本身的迭代与进化\n\n## Wiki 生命周期\n\n```\n初创 → 成长 → 成熟 → 迭代\n```\n\n---\n\n## 各阶段特征\n\n| 阶段 | 特征 | 重点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **初创** | 0-20 页 | 建立结构、Schema |\n| **成长** | 20-100 页 | 完善链接、定期 Lint |\n| **成熟** | 100+ 页 | 自动化、批量处理 |\n| **迭代** | 持续 | 不断优化 |\n\n---\n\n## 当前阶段\n\n| 指标 | 值 | 阶段 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| 实体页 | 39 | 成长 → 成熟 |\n| 链接数 | ~100+ | 成长 |\n| Lint | 已定义 | 建立中 |\n| 使用频率 | 本次开始 | 初创 |\n\n---\n\n## 进化方向\n\n### 短期 (1周)\n\n- [ ] 实际 Ingest 一些内容\n- [ ] 试运行 Query Write-back\n- [ ] 运行首次 Lint\n\n### 中期 (1月)\n\n- [ ] 完善自动化\n- [ ] 添加更多场景页\n- [ ] 建立 Git 备份\n\n### 长期 (3月)\n\n- [ ] 100+ 实体页\n- [ ] 完全习惯 Wiki 工作流\n- [ ] 团队/个人多维度使用\n\n---\n\n## Wiki 自我维护\n\n| 项目 | 自动化程度 |\n|------|-----------|\n| 更新时间戳 | ✅ 自动 |\n| 死链检查 | 手动/未来自动 |\n| 新页面创建 | 半自动 |\n| 内容质量 | 手动 |\n\n---\n\n## 如何评估健康\n\n| 指标 | 目标 |\n|------|------|\n| 页面数量 | 持续增长 |\n\n[15 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776022354532}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5999ebc","parentId":"42514f75","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:40.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a much clearer picture. The LLM task for entity pages was a Wiki Auto-Learning Framework that:\n\n1. Scans knowledge sources (docs/, skills/)\n2. Uses LLM to synthesize and update entity pages\n3. Follows the \"Compilation\" approach vs RAG\n\nThe framework was designed with these core principles:\n- Not RAG, but persistent wiki building\n- Knowledge compiled once, continuously updated\n- One source triggers 10-15 page updates\n- Near zero maintenance cost\n- Human handles source selection, LLM handles maintenance\n- Good answers write back to wiki\n\nLet me check what scripts exist and whether they're actually running.","thinkingSignature":"c9d5f7355f5b3c75fc4a8f227f3a77d813f5c167d25aed8c14e19bce60bfd7e2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n8i7q95q3evl_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py","offset":81,"limit":80}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n8i7q95q3evl_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":105800,"output":234,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124071,"cost":{"input":0.03174,"output":0.0002808,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03310302}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776022354547,"responseId":"062b265196a84e895179774ad16a5ecc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3272bc63","parentId":"e5999ebc","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:40.295Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n8i7q95q3evl_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        }\n        \n        # 根据原文：知识是否与现有 wiki 相关？\n        # 是否值得编译到 wiki？\n        # 是否能增强现有实体页？\n        \n        # 简单判断：与 OpenClaw、Claude Code、Skills 相关则入\n        keywords = [\"claude\", \"code\", \"openclaw\", \"skill\", \"tool\", \"agent\"]\n        if any(k in name.lower() for k in keywords):\n            analysis[\"value\"] = \"high\"\n            analysis[\"action\"] = \"ingest\"\n        \n        return analysis\n    \n    def write_back(self, analysis):\n        \"\"\"3. 写回 (Write-back)\"\"\"\n        if analysis[\"action\"] != \"ingest\":\n            return False\n        \n        # 根据原文：更新实体页、索引、log\n        # 一个 source 最多可影响 10-15 页\n        \n        # 检查是否已有对应实体页\n        entity_name = analysis[\"name\"].lower().replace(\".md\", \"\").replace(\" \", \"-\")\n        entity_file = Path(ENTITIES_DIR) / f\"{entity_name}.md\"\n        \n        if not entity_file.exists():\n            # 创建新实体页\n            content = f\"\"\"---\ntitle: {analysis['name']}\ntype: entity\nstatus: auto-ingested\nlast_updated: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')}\ntags: [auto, {analysis['type']}]\n---\n\n# {analysis['name']}\n\n> 自动从 {analysis['type']} 摄入\n\n## 来源\n\n- 类型: {analysis['type']}\n- 路径: {analysis['name']}\n- 摄入时间: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')}\n\n## 分析\n\n基于 LLM Wiki 原文分析：\n- 价值评估: {analysis['value']}\n- 相关性: {analysis['relevance']}\n\n## 相关页面\n\n- [[llm-wiki]] - LLM Wiki 模式\n- [[ai-usage]] - AI 如何使用\n\"\"\"\n            entity_file.write_text(content, encoding='utf-8')\n            self.log(f\"  📝 创建实体页: {entity_name}\")\n            return True\n        \n        return False\n    \n    def lint_check(self):\n        \"\"\"4. Lint 检查\"\"\"\n        issues = {\n            \"dead_links\": [],\n            \"orphans\": [],\n            \"stale\": []\n        }\n        \n        # 死链检查\n        entity_files = list(Path(ENTITIES_DIR).glob(\"*.md\"))\n        all_links = set()\n        \n        for ef in entity_files:\n            content = ef.read_text(encoding='utf-8')\n            # 提取 [[link]] 格式\n            links = re.findall(r'\\[\\[([a-z0-9-]+)\\]\\]', content)\n            all_links.update(links)\n\n[89 more lines in file. Use offset=161 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776022360282}}
{"type":"message","id":"b75ae6e7","parentId":"3272bc63","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:32:40.308Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n8i7q95q3evl_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# LLM Wiki 7小时自动化学习循环 (修正版)\n# 贯彻需求 + LLM Wiki 原文\n# 区分: skills/ → 实体页 | docs/ → Raw Sources\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nCOUNTER=0\nMAX_ITERATIONS=210  # 7小时\n\necho \"=== 7小时自动化学习循环启动 (修正版) ===\"\necho \"开始: $(date)\"\necho \"规则: skills/→实体页, docs/→Raw Sources\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 确保 raw 目录存在\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\"\n\nwhile [ $COUNTER -lt $MAX_ITERATIONS ]; do\n    COUNTER=$((COUNTER + 1))\n    PERCENT=$((COUNTER * 100 / MAX_ITERATIONS))\n    MINUTE=$((COUNTER * 2))\n    \n    echo \"[$(date +%H:%M:%S)] 循环 $COUNTER/$MAX_ITERATIONS\"\n    \n    # ===== 1. Ingest - 扫描知识源 =====\n    # 只扫描 skills/ 目录创建实体页 (不是 docs/)\n    NEW_ENTITIES=0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":50,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# LLM Wiki 7小时自动化学习循环 (修正版)\n# 贯彻需求 + LLM Wiki 原文\n# 区分: skills/ → 实体页 | docs/ → Raw Sources\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nCOUNTER=0\nMAX_ITERATIONS=210  # 7小时\n\necho \"=== 7小时自动化学习循环启动 (修正版) ===\"\necho \"开始: $(date)\"\necho \"规则: skills/→实体页, docs/→Raw Sources\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 确保 raw 目录存在\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\"\n\nwhile [ $COUNTER -lt $MAX_ITERATIONS ]; do\n    COUNTER=$((COUNTER + 1))\n    PERCENT=$((COUNTER * 100 / MAX_ITERATIONS))\n    MINUTE=$((COUNTER * 2))\n    \n    echo \"[$(date +%H:%M:%S)] 循环 $COUNTER/$MAX_ITERATIONS\"\n    \n    # ===== 1. Ingest - 扫描知识源 =====\n    # 只扫描 skills/ 目录创建实体页 (不是 docs/)\n    NEW_ENTITIES=0","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776022360295}}
