{"type":"message","id":"4a441503","parentId":"821d9d76","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:33:14.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a full picture. The LLM Wiki Auto-Learning framework was a comprehensive system that:\n\n1. Ran on 2026-04-11 from 02:12 to about 03:16 (over an hour of intensive activity)\n2. Created 25 new entity pages from skills/docs sources\n3. Had a 7-hour loop planned (210 iterations) but seemed to have stopped around iteration 2\n4. The wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh script was the main runner that:\n   - Scanned skills/ → created entity pages\n   - Scanned docs/ → put in raw sources\n   - Tried to follow the \"LLM Wiki Pattern\" principles (not RAG, but Compilation)\n5. The auto-learn.py was the Python framework that did the actual LLM-driven synthesis\n\nKey findings:\n- The framework ran once on 2026-04-11 in the early morning hours\n- It created 25 new entity pages (from 33 to 58 entities)\n- But then stopped - the 7-hour loop only ran 2 iterations before being killed/interrupted\n- No cron was ever set up to run these automatically\n- The entities-archive has 80+ archived entities, suggesting a lot of entity churn\n\nThe user is asking about \"之前搞得llm任务，关于实体页的\" - this refers to this LLM Wiki Auto-Learning system that was built to automatically create and maintain entity pages from knowledge sources.\n\nThe current state:\n- The system was designed and ran once\n- It created entity pages but wasn't continuous\n- The scripts exist but aren't in cron\n- The wiki evolution tracking says the current phase is \"成长 → 成熟\" with 39 entity pages (though actual count may differ)\n\nThe core task was: given skills/docs/raw sources → use LLM to create entity pages, update cross-references, maintain the wiki automatically.","thinkingSignature":"3c90a9f08c13e592ab2d65db5822b246fe6692fef1dc12e9337e128008a26e09"},{"type":"text","text":"\n找到了。\n\n---\n\n## LLM Wiki 实体页任务 — 完整还原\n\n**时间：2026-04-11 凌晨 02:12 ~ 03:16**\n\n你建了一套**自动从知识源生成实体页**的框架。\n\n---\n\n### 核心理念\n\n```\n不是 RAG（每次查询重新发现）\n是 Compilation（知识编译一次，持续积累）\n```\n\n一个知识源进来 → 触发 10-15 个实体页更新。\n\n---\n\n### 架构\n\n```\nskills/ → 扫描 → LLM分析 → 创建/更新实体页\ndocs/   → 扫描 → LLM分析 → 存入 Raw Sources\n                    ↓\n              更新交叉引用\n                    ↓\n              写 log.md\n```\n\n---\n\n### 跑了什么\n\n| 脚本 | 做了什么 |\n|------|----------|\n| `wiki-auto-learn.py` | Python框架：扫描→合成→写回→Lint |\n| `wiki-7h-loop-v2.sh` | 主循环：每2分钟跑一轮，共210轮（7小时） |\n| `wiki-7h-loop.sh` | 旧版循环 |\n| `wiki-deep-learn-7h.sh` | 深度学习变体 |\n| `wiki-think-7h.sh` | 思考型变体 |\n\n---\n\n### 实际结果\n\n**02:12** — 开始，entity pages: 27，死链: 8\n**02:14** — entity pages: 28，死链: 2\n**02:16** — entity pages: 30，死链: 0\n**02:22** — `auto-cycle` → entities: 58，**新增: 25**\n**02:24** — entities: 58，新增: 0（停止增长）\n\n然后停了。7小时循环只跑了2轮。\n\n---\n\n### 现在的状态\n\n- 脚本存在，但**没有任何一个在 cron 里**\n- 上次运行是 2026-04-11（2天前）\n- 跑了1次，然后没再触发过\n- 实体页实际数量说法不一——日志说58，wiki-evolution.md说39，entities/目录有25个核心+80+归档\n\n---\n\n### 缺什么\n\n这个框架设计完整，但**跑了1次就停了，没有持续化**。\n\n如果想重新跑起来，只需要加一行 cron：\n\n```bash\n# 每小时跑一次 wiki auto-learn（温和版，不炸资源）\n0 * * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py >> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/wiki-auto-learn.log 2>&1\n```\n\n要我加上吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109196,"output":940,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128173,"cost":{"input":0.0327588,"output":0.0011279999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034969019999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776022371567,"responseId":"062b26631940c2add4f8ffcb61248ef3"}}
