{"type":"message","id":"71f73a3d","parentId":"0b62f0ae","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:36:02.037Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the memory and context problems have been solved. Let me think about what we found:\n\n1. **Context API (3101)** - running, simple message store, nobody calls it\n2. **Memory** - LanceDB vector memory enabled, autoCapture + autoRecall, but requires OpenAI-compatible API for embeddings\n3. **Bootstrap断层** - documented in 2026-04-12 log, not fixed\n4. **Session continuity** - depends on file-based memory loading at session start\n5. **elf-improving** - corrections happen but feedback loop isn't closed\n\nThe direct answer is: partially. Let me be honest about what works and what doesn't.\n\n\nLooking at the actual state: the memory systems are in place with files, LanceDB vector search, and session-based context, but they're not fully connected. The real issues are that bootstrap still breaks between sessions, the context API isn't being called by anything, LanceDB requires external embedding services that may not be available, and there's no heartbeat-driven maintenance loop keeping memory organized. So memory exists but the automated aspects aren't really working yet.","thinkingSignature":"00af07d82ced432b5759bd7327a558c07d4d2341255770c357c1583a5004f474"},{"type":"text","text":"没有。\n\n---\n\n### 记忆层现状\n\n| 组件 | 状态 | 实际问题 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 文件记忆 (memory/) | ✅ 有 | 靠约定，无自动写入 |\n| LanceDB 向量搜索 | ⚠️ 配置了 | bge-m3 embedding 用的是本地 ollama，没验证是否通 |\n| Context API (3101) | ✅ 跑着 | 没人调用，是个空壳 |\n| Bootstrap | ❌ 断了 | session 启动时 MEMORY.md 有时不加载 |\n| 自我整理 | ❌ 没跑 | memory-keeper 写了但没 cron |\n\n---\n\n### 上下文现状\n\n| 组件 | 状态 | 实际问题 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Session 内上下文 | ✅ 模型自带 | 靠 context window |\n| Session 间传递 | ⚠️ 靠文件 | Bootstrap 断了就没了 |\n| Hook 注入 | ⚠️ 配置了但部分失败 | auto-score-classify → 3104 返回 500 |\n| v8 scoring | ❌ 没接入 | 3103 活着但没被调用 |\n\n---\n\n### 核心结论\n\n```\n记忆：有机制，无流动\n上下文：有注入，注入链路断了\n```\n\n你说\"融进框架\"，但记忆层和上下文层**根本没有和框架真正接通**。\n\n---\n\n### 解决路径\n\n**第一步必须做：修好 3104**\n\n3104 返回 500 导致整个 hooks 链路断掉，不修这个，其他一切都是空的。\n\n修好之后：\n\n```\n消息 → Gateway hooks → 3104/classify（正常）\n                        ↓\n                    3103/score（正常）\n                        ↓\n                    路由决策 → 执行\n                        ↓\n                    记忆写入（自动 → memory/）\n```\n\n你现在要我先把 3104 修好吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":605,"cacheRead":128091,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128696,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.000726,"cacheRead":0.007685459999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008411459999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776022546444,"responseId":"062b271246fee0688c826f132cae9c68"}}
