{"type":"message","id":"bc86b6db","parentId":"4c77bd17","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:38:43.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a comprehensive think and a plan. Let me do a thorough analysis of the entire situation, covering all the gaps found, and produce a prioritized action plan. I should be systematic and honest.","thinkingSignature":"b74a256f85e3e92def87d8b99495241f581e3ccc074887be5367cbcc854ead7a"},{"type":"text","text":"好。全面想完，说方案。\n\n---\n\n## 当前真实状态\n\n```\n三层系统各自为战：\nGateway(18789/3102) ← 活着，AI在跑\nopenclaw-router(3102) ← 死了(dotenv+3108)\nv8引擎(3103) ← 活着，没人调用\ncontext-api(3101) ← 活着，没人调用\nscene-classifier(3104) ← 500错，基本死了\n\n记忆/上下文层：\nBootstrap ← 间歇性断\nLanceDB ← 配置了，不知道通不通\nmemory-keeper ← 装了，没cron\nwiki-auto-learn ← 跑了1次就停了\n```\n\n---\n\n## 问题链\n\n```\n① 3104(classifier) 500错\n  → hooks: auto-score-classify 失效\n  → 所有消息不走分类评分直连\n  → v8引擎(3103) 完全空转\n\n② openclaw-router 死\n  → ws-proxy 指向不存在的3108\n  → 流量路由规则无效\n  → 天气脚本往未配置的飞书群发\n\n③ Bootstrap 断\n  → session间记忆丢失\n  → 上一轮做的事下次不记得\n\n④ 记忆层无流动\n  → wiki-auto-learn 跑了1次停了\n  → memory-keeper 没cron\n  → corrections闭环没通\n\n⑤ ws-proxy 的 3108 错\n  → 即修复dotenv也会死于端口错\n```\n\n---\n\n## 完整方案（按优先级）\n\n### P0 — 让系统重新连通\n\n**Step 1：修 3104（scene-classifier）**\n```\n查日志：\n  /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/logs/\n  /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/logs/\n\n常见原因：\n  - HF模型下载失败/路径错\n  - pipeline初始化异常\n  - Python依赖缺\n```\n\n**Step 2：修 openclaw-router**\n```\ncd /home/ai/openclaw-router && npm install dotenv\nsed -i 's/localhost:3108/localhost:3102/g' openclaw-router.js ws-proxy.js\nsystemctl restart openclaw-router openclaw-ws-proxy\n```\n\n**Step 3：验证连通**\n```\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3104/classify \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"text\":\"帮我写一个备份脚本\"}'\n\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"text\":\"帮我写一个备份脚本\"}'\n```\n\n---\n\n### P1 — 让记忆层自动跑起来\n\n**Step 4：加 cron（最简单立刻见效）**\n```\n# 每小时增量 ingest（温和版）\n0 * * * * cd /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace && python3 scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py --mode=ingest --limit=3 >> logs/wiki-ingest.log 2>&1\n\n# 每日 Lint + 整理\n0 3 * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-lint.sh && /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_keeper.sh >> logs/memory-maintain.log 2>&1\n\n# 每5分钟健康检查（异常时告警）\n*/5 * * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/health-check.py >> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/health.log 2>&1\n```\n\n**Step 5：修 Bootstrap**\n```\n在 ~/memory/ 下建 session-bootstrap-log.md\nsession 启动时写一行：\n  [timestamp] session=X loaded=[file list] ok=true/false\n\n在 AGENTS.md 启动流程里加一行写入动作\n```\n\n---\n\n### P2 — 让上下文和任务层接通\n\n**Step 6：打通 v8引擎调用链**\n```\n修复①后，hooks: auto-score-classify 自然恢复\n但需要验证 v8 scorer 评分结果是否真的被用来路由\n\n检查：tail -f /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/logs/openclaw.log\n发一条消息，看有没有 task started 日志\n```\n\n**Step 7：修天气脚本**\n```\n方案A：配飞书（如果有真实群ID）\n方案B：关掉（每日8点发往无效群）\n  crontab -e → 删除 0 8 * * * 那行\n```\n\n---\n\n### P3 — 长期架构对齐\n\n**Step 8：wiki-auto-learn 接入 task_orchestrator**\n```\n给 wiki-auto-learn.py 加 --api 端口模式\n在 task_orchestrator SKILL.md 注册 wiki_ingest 工具\n用户说\"学习这个\"→触发skill→写实体页\n```\n\n**Step 9：workspace 备份**\n```\ncd /home/ai/.openclaw && git add -A && git commit -m \"backup $(date)\"\n加到每日cron里\n```\n\n---\n\n## 执行顺序\n\n```\n今天（10分钟）：\n  ① 修3104查日志\n  ② 修router+改3108\n  ③ 验证curl\n\n明天（30分钟）：\n  ④ 加3条cron\n  ⑤ 建bootstrap日志\n  ⑥ 修/关天气脚本\n\n本周（1小时）：\n  ⑦ 验证hooks链路通了\n  ⑧ wiki-auto-learn --api 模式\n  ⑨ git备份cron\n```\n\n---\n\n## 唯一判断\n\n**修好①和②之后，框架才能真正开始自动。**\n\n不修这两样，加再多 cron 也是在空跑。开始做吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":1227,"cacheRead":128647,"cacheWrite":164,"totalTokens":130092,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0014724,"cacheRead":0.0077188199999999995,"cacheWrite":0.0000615,"total":0.00926892}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776022696977,"responseId":"062b27a80a3699a19e8dd1ee76b2d7ce"}}
